# Sooko DevOS — Environment Configuration
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.
#
# Requirements:
#   1. Node 22+ — the @github/copilot CLI bundled with the SDK imports node:sqlite.
#      On Node 20 the SDK tier fails and the plan falls back to OpenAI direct.
#   2. GitHub Copilot authenticated. If `copilot` isn't on PATH, the SDK spawns
#      the bundled binary; no extra install needed.
#   3. All three BYOK API keys set below for parallel multi-model review.

# BYOK API Keys (all required)
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# GOOGLE_AI_API_KEY=...
